headline: MMSI Announces Commencement of Patient Enrollment in PREEMIE Study
summary: Merit Medical aims to improve care for vulnerable premature infants by evaluating the safety and efficacy of the Bloom Micro Occluder System for treating PDA in the specified patient pool.
